title: Condo 2 bedrooms 2.5 bathrooms in Brickell
posting_body: ['Beautiful and spacious 2 beds/2.5 Baths with plenty closets.', 'Spacious balcony facing north with access from every room.', 'Views to Miami Skyline, Miami River and glimpses of the Biscayne Bay.', 'This is unit is ready to move-in, features an open design kitchen, stainless steel appliances, washer/dryer, etc.', 'Great location, walking distance Metro Rail, Brickell City Center, Mary Brickell, Supermarket, Restaurants and all Brickell nightlife.', 'This full service condominium with great amenities that includes 2 level gym, pool, business center, concierge service and more.', 'Rent includes basic cable and internet, 1 assigned parking (valet) and additional parking is available for rent with Valet Company.', 'Please contact Fred Ardjmand Licensed Real Estate Associate', 'show contact info', '/ One Stop Realty', 'Listing Courtesy of JBV Advisors']
